info.description:
# Introduction
This collection interacts with Order Service APIs (OG, Adyen, Paypal, Avalara)

# Overview
Every request requires Request body

# Authentication
There is no Authentication requried but you must send sender as paramiter

# Error Codes
404 if request is bad and 500 if internal error happens

# Rate limit
There is no limit how many request you can send but if you send reqeust in production please be careful as you may slow down orderservice and you will hit production OG, Adyen and Avalara

# Parameters
To test some of the end points, we have to update parameters based on the api end points. Parameters are used inside {{}}. To change this you have to go to each Environments and update those values and click Save.

# Comments
Some of the end points has specific instructions to run. For example you have to update the parameters. Look at the comment sections farther instruction.
